 2025-01652025-02-25FIN, MINT
ActRoyal Canadian Mint Act
SubjectOrder Authorizing the Issue of Two Two-dollar Commemorative Circulation Coins Specifying the Characteristics and Determining the Designs (Tomb of Unknown Soldier)
PrecisOrder authorizing the Royal Canadian Mint to produce two TWO-DOLLAR commemorative circulation coins in order to honour Canada’s Unknown Soldier and to recognize all of those who have died serving, as well as all those who serve, or have served, Canada in a military capacity.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 2025-0040 Publication Date: 2025-03-12
